---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FlowMind AI - 智能论文流程图生成器">
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>FlowMind AI</h1>
        <h2>智能论文流程图生成器</h2>
        <p>
          AI驱动的学术论文到PowerPoint流程图自动生成系统，让您的研究成果更加直观、专业
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/product" class="cta-button primary">产品展示</a>
          <a href="/flowchart" class="cta-button primary">立即体验</a>
          <a href="/about" class="cta-button secondary">了解更多</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features">
      <h2>核心功能</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
          <h3>论文解析</h3>
          <p>支持PDF文件上传或直接文本输入，自动提取关键流程信息。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
          <h3>智能流程图生成</h3>
          <p>使用先进的AI模型将文本转换为Mermaid格式的流程图。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">😀</div>
          <h3>表情符号增强</h3>
          <p>自动为流程图节点添加相关的表情符号，提高可读性和视觉吸引力。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>PowerPoint导出</h3>
          <p>一键导出为专业的PowerPoint演示文稿，节省手动创建流程图的时间。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="pricing">
      <h2>定价方案</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>免费试用</h3>
          <div class="price">¥0</div>
          <ul>
            <li>首次使用完全免费</li>
            <li>体验所有核心功能</li>
            <li>最多处理1篇论文</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/flowchart" class="cta-button primary">立即试用</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <h3>基础套餐</h3>
          <div class="price">¥50</div>
          <ul>
            <li>10次使用额度</li>
            <li>所有核心功能</li>
            <li>优先处理</li>
            <li>基础技术支持</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary">立即购买</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>专业套餐</h3>
          <div class="price">¥200</div>
          <ul>
            <li>50次使用额度</li>
            <li>所有高级功能</li>
            <li>优先处理</li>
            <li>专业技术支持</li>
            <li>自定义模板</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary">立即购买</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="appointment-note">要使用我们的服务，请通过官方网站预约。</p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="academic-support">
      <h2>学术支持</h2>
      <img src="/images/westlake_logo.svg" alt="西湖大学" class="university-logo">
      <p>本项目得到西湖大学的学术支持，致力于推动科研成果的可视化和知识传播。</p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="contact">
      <h2>联系我们</h2>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><strong>开发者</strong>: Joey Sun</p>
        <p><strong>邮箱</strong>: giao_giao@hotmail.com</p>
        <p><strong>GitHub</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/giao-123-sun/dofanxin">https://github.com/giao-123-sun/dofanxin</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d, #2a4365);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .cta-button.primary {
    background-color: #4299e1;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .cta-button.primary:hover {
    background-color: #3182ce;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .cta-button.secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid white;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .cta-button.secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .features {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .features h2, .pricing h2, .academic-support h2, .contact h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .feature-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .feature-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
  
  /* Pricing Section */
  .pricing {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  
  .pricing-card.featured {
    background-color: #ebf8ff;
    border: 2px solid #4299e1;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .pricing-card.featured:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .pricing-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .pricing-card ul {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #4a5568;
  }
  
  .appointment-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #718096;
  }
  
  /* Academic Support Section */
  .academic-support {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: #f7fafc;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .university-logo {
    max-width: 200px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .academic-support p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #4a5568;
  }
  
  /* Contact Section */
  .contact {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: #2d3748;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .contact h2 {
    color: white;
  }
  
  .contact-info {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .contact-info a {
    color: #4299e1;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .pricing-card.featured {
      transform: none;
    }
    
    .pricing-card.featured:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
  }
</style>
